   <description>This is a collection of notebooks that together show
    how to use Python to retrieve data from VO services.  There are
    science use case examples as well as tutorials that specifically
    deal with each type of service.  There is also a single summary
    cheat-sheet.  This resource is produced by the NASA Astronomical
    Virtual Observatories.</description>
